# Frontend Environment Variables Configuration

# Backend API URL (for production deployment)
# Local development: http://127.0.0.1:8000 (Vite dev proxy handles this)
# Production: https://your-backend-api-domain.com (set in Vercel)
VITE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000

# Example configurations:

# ╔════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║ LOCAL DEVELOPMENT (no need to set, default works)              ║
# ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║ VITE_API_URL defaults to http://127.0.0.1:8000                 ║
# ║ Vite dev server proxies /api to http://127.0.0.1:8000/api      ║
# ╚════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

# ╔════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║ PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT (Vercel)                                  ║
# ╠════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
# ║ Set in Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables     ║
# ║ VITE_API_URL=https://finances-api.onrender.com                 ║
# ║ (or your Render backend URL)                                    ║
# ╚════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

